data.description: Exquisite 4-Bedroom Home in the Coveted Neufairfield Community  This stunning 4-bedroom, 3 1/2 bath residence nestled in the highly sought-after Neufairfield Community. As you step inside, be captivated by the spaciousness and elegance this home offers. A grand family room with fireplace sets the tone. Open kitchen has beautiful cabinets and showcases gorgeous hardwood flooring that extends throughout the main level. An inviting office space awaits, providing the perfect area for work or study. Upstairs, discover a generously sized loft area, an ideal versatile space that can cater to various needs. Second floor laundry. The master suite is a retreat of its own, featuring a walk-in closet and a private bath, luxurious tub and a separate shower. The lower level boasts a fully finished basement, complete with a stage and a dedicated workout area, complemented by a full bathroom. This space offers endless possibilities for entertainment, hobbies, or relaxation.  Outside has fenced backyard, for kids, and pets to enjoy. The hot tub creates an inviting oasis of relaxation.  Located in the esteemed New Lenox school district, this residence offers not just a home, but a lifestyle of comfort and convenience, surrounded by excellent educational opportunities and community amenities.  Don't miss the chance to make this exquisite property your own. Contact me for your private showing today!
